                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>As a you will be scoring the student's proposal based on a few key elements.</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Does the project demonstrate experiential learning in a CSTEM discipline?</li>
                                        <li>Is the budget realistic and justified in the project description?</li>
                                        <li>Are the proposed methods appropriate to achieve the goals of the project?</li>
                                        <li>Is the proposed timeline reasonable?</li>
                                        <li>Is the project well explained (including rationale) and justified?</li>
                                        <li>Does the budget only include eligible activities (supplies, equipment, field/conference travel)?</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <br>
                                    <p>If you are ready to begin review student applications, click below!</p>
<a href="login.php?id=reviewer" class="btn btn-primary" id="reviewer">Faculty Reviewer</a>
